@NODE levels "About the levels"

This level set consists of 15 levels. The difficulty is increasing from 
easy/medium to hard. All levels can be played by one player as well as by two
players. In two player mode use for best results at least resolution 640×512
if you have the possibility. There are also record files included. They show how
to successfully finish the levels in one and in two player modus. If you want to
really enjoy playing these levels DON'T view the record files unless you are
stuck. Although the set includes only 15 levels, you'll play them for quite a
while because they are not easy neither short.

The highscores aren't cleared because otherwise all the record files wouldn't
work correctly (It's the fault of Diamond Caves and not mine). Because you are a
registered user you can clear them yourself using the editor but in this case
some of the record files won't show the correct solutions. Sorry, but it really
isn't my fault.

@{"Install the levels" LINK installation} and start playing!

