@NODE installation "How to install this level set?"

The installation is very simple. Just click on the install icon in this drawer.
It's completely automatical. The install program assumes that you have an
assign named DC: You certainly have it if you have the Diamond Caves installed
(otherwise you don't need this level set anyway;-).

