@NODE contacts "How (and why) to contact me?"

Since you're reading this document I assume you are going to play (or have
already played) these levels.

In this case I ask you to send me your opinion about my levels. Tell me if you
like them or not. Tell me what you like and what you dislike. Do you think the
levels are to easy or are they to hard? Should the next set contain more levels?
You may add some comments of your own. If you really feel generous and you
really like my levels and want to encourage me in making new ones, you can even
send me some money. I wouldn't reject it;-)


@{b}@{u}Why do I need this responses?@{ub}@{uu}

I intent to design further levels and I need to know how the players like
these levels so that the next set will be better for everyone:-)


@{b}@{u}What do you get in exchange for your responses?@{ub}@{uu}

Everybody who is going to contact me will be mentioned in the next level set.
It's not much but it's better than nothing. And don't forget my eternal
gratitude;-)


