@NODE autumn "What is Autumn Design?"

@{b}Autumn Design@{ub} is the name under which I intent to release my amiga products.
This is my first one but it certainly won't be the only one. I'll release
levels for other amiga games (Pacman 96, Crazy Balls, Emerald Mines,...). I
also want to make a graphic adventure using GRAAL but for this I'll probably
need some help (read below). I plan some translations of programs and games to
my native language (slovene) because there is a great lack of these
translations. That's for the plans.

Currently I am the only person in Autumn design but I hope it won't stay like
that. I'm looking for a graphician and a musician.


@{b}What a strange name?@{ub}

It comes from my home town Jesenice. "jesen" in my native language means autumn.
But the name of the town comes from a certain tree. The leaves of that tree are
in the background of the @{"logo" LINK logo.pic/main}.

